These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: 7up, milk, hot-chocolate, coffee
Sport: swimming, badminton, tennis, volleyball
1. Beverage:7up is on the right of Sport:tennis##1
2. Sport:volleyball is on the far left##1
3. Sport:tennis is between Sport:badminton and Beverage:milk##2
4. Beverage:coffee is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:hot-chocolate is between Beverage:milk and Beverage:7up##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | coffee         | milk   | hot-chocolate | 7up       |
| Sport      | volleyball | swimming | tennis   | badminton |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: sudoku, singing, chess, traveling
Nationality: mexican, indian, argentine, pakistani
1. Nationality:pakistani is between Hobby:chess and Nationality:indian##2
2. Hobby:traveling is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:argentine is on the right of Nationality:mexican##1
4. Hobby:sudoku is on the left of Nationality:mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | singing | sudoku | chess | traveling |
| Nationality   | indian    | pakistani   | mexican | argentine       |

