3. Nationality:indian is on the far left##1
4. Nationality:german is on the left of Food:cherry##1
5. Food:asparagus == Nationality:german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | pear    | avocado | asparagus   | cherry  |
| Nationality   | indian | pakistani   | german | polish |

